---
title: Harissa Aioli
source: https://flavorfulife.com/harissa-aioli/
---

Whisk together @mayonnaise{1/2%cup}, @harissa paste{1%tbsp}, @smoked paprika{1/2%tsp}, @garlic cloves{2} (finely grated), @lemon juice{1%tbsp}, and @salt and pepper{} to taste. If you prefer a thinner consistency, whisk in @water{1-3%tbsp} until desired texture is reached. Serve as a dipping sauce or spread.
